
Empire Help
~~~~~~~~~~~
Make an [A]nnouncement : Lets you have
   any comments you'd care to make put
   in the Recent Happenings file.

[C]hange Empire's Name : If you need
   help for this, you're in trouble.

Send [M]essage to Another Player : Lets
   you send a private message to the
   player of your choice.

[S]tatus of the Empire : Shows your
   empire's stats.

Increase [T]echnology Level : Spends
   technology units to increase your
   empire's Technology Level.
